    {
      "id": "b1ec6b17_c166f940",
      "file_path": "cps-ncmp-service/src/main/java/org/onap/cps/ncmp/api/inventory/NetworkCmProxyInventoryFacade.java",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 183,
      "message": "Correct, but this is not the only place which applies currentTrustLevel. There is also a method in the same which used by query cm handle APIs on line 139:\n    \n    public Collection<NcmpServiceCmHandle> executeCmHandleSearch(\n        final CmHandleQueryApiParameters cmHandleQueryApiParameters)",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 8063,
        "name": "Halil Cakal",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "halil.cakal@est.tech",
        "username": "halil.cakal"
      },
